      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that u aren't a doctor but it's just so expensive to go to the clinic right now and the wait times are insane. it's probably just a bad sprain, right? like, i've had sprains before and they always feel like this at first. if i just keep it iced and elevated for like 48 hours, shouldn't that be enough to tell if it's serious?",
